caption: If you are on the hunt for a 1965 single family house with 3 floors of living space, parking/garage, in a HOT neighborhood and a great school district, AND central air... then look no further!! Welcome to 223 Avenue B, located in uptown Bayonne just one block to the gorgeous Hudson County Park. This multi generational family home boasts 3 bed 3 bath, a full walk out basement, a 2 car garage (private driveway), hardwood floors, and great bones throughout.
